---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout
  title="About - Servando Torres"
  description="Learn more about Servando Torres"
>
  <article class="about">
    <h1>About Me</h1>

    <div class="about-content">
      <p>
        Hi, I'm Servando Torres, and I'm passionate about artificial
        intelligence, machine learning, and technology. This blog is where I
        share my insights, experiments, and learnings from working in the AI
        space.
      </p>

      <p>
        I believe in learning in public and sharing knowledge with the
        community. Here you'll find posts about AI engineering, machine learning
        experiments, technical tutorials, and thoughts on the future of
        technology.
      </p>

      <h2>What You'll Find Here</h2>
      <ul>
        <li>
          <strong>AI & ML Insights:</strong> Practical applications and learnings
        </li>
        <li>
          <strong>Technical Tutorials:</strong> Step-by-step guides and how-tos
        </li>
        <li>
          <strong>Experiments:</strong> Projects and prototypes I'm working on
        </li>
        <li>
          <strong>Industry Thoughts:</strong> Perspectives on technology trends
        </li>
      </ul>

      <h2>Connect With Me</h2>
      <p>
        Feel free to reach out if you want to discuss AI, collaborate on
        projects, or just say hello!
      </p>

      <div class="contact-links">
        <a href="https://github.com/vandotorres" target="_blank" rel="noopener"
          >GitHub</a
        >
        <a href="https://x.com/vandotorres" target="_blank" rel="noopener"
          >Twitter</a
        >
        <a href="mailto:servando@example.com">Email</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </article>
</Layout>

<style>
  .about {
    max-width: 700px;
  }

  .about-content p {
    font-size: 1.125rem;
    line-height: 1.7;
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
  }

  .about-content h2 {
    margin-top: 2.5rem;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
    color: var(--text-primary);
  }

  .about-content ul {
    margin: 1rem 0 2rem 2rem;
  }

  .about-content li {
    margin: 0.75rem 0;
    line-height: 1.6;
  }

  .contact-links {
    display: flex;
    gap: 1.5rem;
    margin-top: 2.5rem;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
  }

  .contact-links a {
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    padding: 0.75rem 1.5rem;
    background-color: var(--bg-secondary);
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
    border-radius: 0.75rem;
    color: var(--text-primary) !important;
    font-weight: 500;
    transition: all 0.2s;
    text-decoration: none;
  }

  .contact-links a:hover {
    border-color: var(--accent);
    background-color: var(--accent);
    color: white !important;
    transform: translateY(-2px);
    box-shadow: 0 4px 12px rgba(59, 130, 246, 0.25);
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .contact-links {
      flex-direction: column;
      gap: 1rem;
    }

    .contact-links a {
      text-align: center;
    }
  }
</style>
